title: Mocha Cabana
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Macrobiotic, Thai, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers vegan/vegetarian and gluten free options ona separate menu with all easily veganized items marked with a V. Uses locally grown foods when possible. Once or twice a year, possibly more in the future, holds an all weekend (Fri-Sun) 3-course completely vegan meal option including maple-rum cheesecake with vanilla cashew whip. Has local singers and groups playing live; check schedule.
